text: __NOTOC__ Location of Pickens County in Alabama This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in Pickens County, Alabama. This is intended to be a complete list of the properties and districts on the National Register of Historic Places in Pickens County, Alabama, United States. Latitude and longitude coordinates are provided for many National Register properties and districts; these locations may be seen together in a Google map. There are 7 properties and districts listed on the National Register in the county. |} ==See also== * List of National Historic Landmarks in Alabama * National Register of Historic Places listings in Alabama ==References== Pickens
